ru-tts (3.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added postinst script that generates ru_RU.koi8r locale if
    necessary.
  * Building and running in x86_64 environment.
  * Don't require locale if it is not actually needed.
  * Raise an error when ru_RU.koi8r locale is required but not
    available.
  * Return failure code when unknown option is specified.
  * Updated packaging standards compliance.
  * Updated rulex dependency.

 -- Igor B. Poretsky <poretsky@mlbox.ru>  Sun, 23 Sep 2012 16:11:05 +0400

