ru-tts (2.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Speech rate tuning now affects gaps between words as well, so quick
    speech sounds more smoothly.
  * More strict command line parameters parsing and default values
    revision.

 -- Igor B. Poretsky <poretsky@mlbox.ru>  Sat, 27 Feb 2010 00:58:18 +0300

ru-tts (2.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Switch to the new lexical database structure implementing some rules
    and implicit form construction mechanism.
  * Use default version of the Berkeley database support library instead
    of the explicit one.
  * Increased speech rate.
  * Switch ru_speak from sox to aplay.
  * Separate description in Russian.

 -- Igor B. Poretsky <poretsky@mlbox.ru>  Thu, 11 Feb 2010 01:48:35 +0300

